data.description: Great investment opportunity for an investor, developer or owner occupied buyer. The building contains 3 Studios and one 2 Bedroom 1 Bath unit. Located in the Willmore City Historic District in the North Pine neighborhood is primarily made up of small (studio to two bedroom) to medium sized (three or four bedroom) apartment complexes / high-rise apartments and small apartment buildings. Most of the residential real estate is renter occupied so perfect for that investor seeking residential income. New separate meters installed recently and all new copper plumbing about to be installed before close of escrow. Also newly painted exterior.
